<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Trial is Ending Soon - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">⏰ Your Trial is Ending Soon</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{ownerName}},</p>

    <p>Your 30-day Standard tier trial for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> will expire soon.</p>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #FF9800; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #f57c00;">Trial Status:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Days Remaining:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #f57c00; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">{{daysRemaining}} days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Expires On:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">{{trialEndsAt}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Current Tier:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">Standard (Trial)</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>What happens when your trial ends?</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>❌ Your account will automatically downgrade to the Free tier</li>
      <li>❌ Free tier limits: 3 tables, 20 menu items, 1 staff, 100 orders/month</li>
      <li>❌ Some advanced features will be disabled</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <strong>Good news!</strong> Upgrade now to continue enjoying all Standard or Premium features without interruption.
    </p>

    <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Upgrade Options:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 12px; border: 2px solid #4CAF50; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; width: 50%;">
            <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #4CAF50;">Standard</strong><br>
            <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">$240</span>/year<br>
            <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">($20/month)</span>
          </td>
          <td style="width: 20px;"></td>
          <td style="padding: 12px; border: 2px solid #FFD700; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; width: 50%;">
            <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF9800;">Premium</strong><br>
            <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">$1200</span>/year<br>
            <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">($100/month)</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{upgradeUrl}}" style="background: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
        Upgrade Now
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      Questions about upgrading? Contact us at support@originfoodhouse.com
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
